data.description: Welcome home to this charming waterfront Cape cod in the Old Wythe neighborhood of Hampton. Enjoy Indian River by kayak or paddle board, and fishing or crabbing in your backyard. So much wildlife to see and only blocks over from the Chesapeake Bay with direct access. This spacious home offers an updated kitchen with newer SS appliances, and lots of cabinet space.  A huge finished room over the 2 car garage that could be a 4th bedroom, game room or office space. This home sets on a large .30 acre waterfront lot, with a gravel circular driveway. There is much to see, with so much character!  Seller is highly motivated!
